{"ps3.10:0.1":"Patisambhidamagga ","ps3.10:0.2":"3 Pannavagga ","ps3.10:0.3":"3.10. Matikakatha ","ps3.10:1.1":"Nicchato, mokkho vimokkho, vijjavimutti, adhisilam, adhicittam, adhipanna, passaddhi, nanam, dassanam, visuddhi, nekkhammam, nissaranam, paviveko, vosaggo, cariya, jhanavimokkho, bhavana, adhitthanam, jivitam. [19] ","ps3.10:2.1":"<b>Nicchato</b>ti nekkhammena kamacchandato nicchato, abyapadena byapadato nicchato …pe… ","ps3.10:2.2":"pathamena jhanena nivaranehi nicchato …pe… ","ps3.10:2.3":"arahattamaggena sabbakilesehi nicchato. ","ps3.10:3.1":"<b>Mokkho vimokkho</b>ti nekkhammena kamacchandato muccatiti—","ps3.10:3.2":"mokkho vimokkho. ","ps3.10:3.3":"Abyapadena byapadato muccatiti—","ps3.10:3.4":"mokkho vimokkho …pe… ","ps3.10:3.5":"pathamena jhanena nivaranehi muccatiti—","ps3.10:3.6":"mokkho vimokkho …pe… ","ps3.10:3.7":"arahattamaggena sabbakilesehi muccatiti—","ps3.10:3.8":"mokkho vimokkho. ","ps3.10:4.1":"<b>Vijjavimutti</b>ti nekkhammam vijjatiti vijja, kamacchandato muccatiti vimutti. ","ps3.10:4.2":"Vijjanto muccati, muccanto vijjatiti—","ps3.10:4.3":"vijjavimutti. ","ps3.10:4.4":"Abyapado vijjatiti vijja, byapadato vimuccatiti vimutti. ","ps3.10:4.5":"Vijjanto muccati, muccanto vijjatiti—","ps3.10:4.6":"vijjavimutti …pe… ","ps3.10:4.7":"arahattamaggo vijjatiti vijja, sabbakilesehi muccatiti vimutti. ","ps3.10:4.8":"Vijjanto muccati, muccanto vijjatiti—","ps3.10:4.9":"vijjavimutti. ","ps3.10:5.1":"<b>Adhisilam adhicittam adhipanna</b>ti nekkhammena kamacchandam, samvaratthena silavisuddhi, avikkhepatthena cittavisuddhi, dassanatthena ditthivisuddhi. ","ps3.10:5.2":"Yo tattha samvarattho, ayam adhisilasikkha. ","ps3.10:5.3":"Yo tattha avikkhepattho, ayam adhicittasikkha. ","ps3.10:5.4":"Yo tattha dassanattho, ayam adhipannasikkha. ","ps3.10:5.5":"Abyapadena byapadam samvaratthena silavisuddhi …pe… ","ps3.10:5.6":"arahattamaggena sabbakilese samvaratthena silavisuddhi, avikkhepatthena cittavisuddhi. ","ps3.10:5.7":"Dassanatthena ditthivisuddhi. ","ps3.10:5.8":"Yo tattha samvarattho, ayam adhisilasikkha. ","ps3.10:5.9":"Yo tattha avikkhepattho, ayam adhicittasikkha. ","ps3.10:5.10":"Yo tattha dassanattho, ayam adhipannasikkha. ","ps3.10:6.1":"<b>Passaddhi</b>ti nekkhammena kamacchandam patippassambheti, abyapadena byapadam patippassambheti …pe… ","ps3.10:6.2":"arahattamaggena sabbakilese patippassambheti. ","ps3.10:7.1":"<b>Nanan</b>ti kamacchandassa pahinatta nekkhammam natatthena nanam; ","ps3.10:7.2":"byapadassa pahinatta abyapado natatthena nanam …pe… ","ps3.10:7.3":"sabbakilesanam pahinatta arahattamaggo natatthena nanam. ","ps3.10:8.1":"<b>Dassanan</b>ti kamacchandassa pahinatta nekkhammam ditthatta dassanam. ","ps3.10:8.2":"Byapadassa pahinatta abyapado ditthatta dassanam …pe… ","ps3.10:8.3":"sabbakilesanam pahinatta arahattamaggo ditthatta dassanam. ","ps3.10:9.1":"<b>Visuddhi</b>ti kamacchandam pajahanto nekkhammena visujjhati. ","ps3.10:9.2":"Byapadam pajahanto abyapadena visujjhati …pe… ","ps3.10:9.3":"sabbakilese pajahanto arahattamaggena visujjhati. ","ps3.10:10.1":"<b>Nekkhamman</b>ti kamanametam nissaranam, yadidam nekkhammam. ","ps3.10:10.2":"Rupanametam nissaranam, yadidam aruppam. ","ps3.10:10.3":"Yam kho pana kinci bhutam sankhatam paticcasamuppannam, nirodho tassa nekkhammam. ","ps3.10:10.4":"Byapadassa abyapado nekkhammam. ","ps3.10:10.5":"Thinamiddhassa alokasanna nekkhammam …pe… ","ps3.10:10.6":"sabbakilesanam arahattamaggo nekkhammam. ","ps3.10:11.1":"<b>Nissaranan</b>ti kamanametam nissaranam, yadidam nekkhammam. ","ps3.10:11.2":"Rupanametam nissaranam, yadidam aruppam. ","ps3.10:11.3":"Yam kho pana kinci bhutam sankhatam paticcasamuppannam, nirodho tassa nissaranam. ","ps3.10:11.4":"Kamacchandassa nekkhammam nissaranam. ","ps3.10:11.5":"Byapadassa abyapado nissaranam …pe… ","ps3.10:11.6":"sabbakilesanam arahattamaggo nissaranam. ","ps3.10:12.1":"<b>Paviveko</b>ti kamacchandassa nekkhammam paviveko …pe… ","ps3.10:12.2":"sabbakilesanam arahattamaggo paviveko. ","ps3.10:13.1":"<b>Vosaggo</b>ti nekkhammena kamacchandam vosajjatiti—","ps3.10:13.2":"vosaggo. ","ps3.10:13.3":"Abyapadena byapadam vosajjatiti—","ps3.10:13.4":"vosaggo …pe… ","ps3.10:13.5":"arahattamaggena sabbakilese vosajjatiti—","ps3.10:13.6":"vosaggo. ","ps3.10:14.1":"<b>Cariya</b>ti kamacchandam pajahanto nekkhammena carati. ","ps3.10:14.2":"Byapadam pajahanto abyapadena carati …pe… ","ps3.10:14.3":"sabbakilese pajahanto arahattamaggena carati. ","ps3.10:15.1":"<b>Jhanavimokkho</b>ti nekkhammam jhayatiti—","ps3.10:15.2":"jhanam. ","ps3.10:15.3":"Kamacchandam jhapetiti—","ps3.10:15.4":"jhanam. ","ps3.10:15.5":"Jhayanto muccatiti—","ps3.10:15.6":"jhanavimokkho. ","ps3.10:15.7":"Jhapento muccatiti—","ps3.10:15.8":"jhanavimokkho. ","ps3.10:15.9":"Jhayantiti dhamma. ","ps3.10:15.10":"Jhapentiti kilese. ","ps3.10:15.11":"Jhate ca jhape ca janatiti—","ps3.10:15.12":"jhanajhayi. ","ps3.10:15.13":"Abyapado jhayatiti jhanam. ","ps3.10:15.14":"Byapadam jhapetiti—","ps3.10:15.15":"jhanam …pe… ","ps3.10:15.16":"alokasanna jhayatiti—","ps3.10:15.17":"jhanam. ","ps3.10:15.18":"Thinamiddham jhapetiti—","ps3.10:15.19":"jhanam …pe… ","ps3.10:15.20":"arahattamaggo jhayatiti—","ps3.10:15.21":"jhanam. ","ps3.10:15.22":"Sabbakilese jhapetiti—","ps3.10:15.23":"jhanam. ","ps3.10:15.24":"Jhayanto muccatiti—","ps3.10:15.25":"jhanavimokkho. ","ps3.10:15.26":"Jhapento muccatiti—","ps3.10:15.27":"jhanavimokkho. ","ps3.10:15.28":"Jhayantiti—","ps3.10:15.29":"dhamma. ","ps3.10:15.30":"Jhapentiti—","ps3.10:15.31":"kilese. ","ps3.10:15.32":"Jhate ca jhape ca janatiti—","ps3.10:15.33":"jhanajhayi. ","ps3.10:16.1":"<b>Bhavana adhitthanam jivitan</b>ti kamacchandam pajahanto nekkhammam bhavetiti—","ps3.10:16.2":"bhavanasampanno. ","ps3.10:16.3":"Nekkhammavasena cittam adhitthatiti—","ps3.10:16.4":"adhitthanasampanno. ","ps3.10:16.5":"Svayam evam bhavanasampanno adhitthanasampanno samam jivati, no visamam; ","ps3.10:16.6":"samma jivati, no miccha; ","ps3.10:16.7":"visuddham jivati, no kilitthanti—","ps3.10:16.8":"ajivasampanno. ","ps3.10:16.9":"Svayam evam bhavanasampanno adhitthanasampanno ajivasampanno yannadeva parisam upasankamati—","ps3.10:16.10":"yadi khattiyaparisam yadi brahmanaparisam yadi gahapatiparisam yadi samanaparisam—","ps3.10:16.11":"visarado upasankamati amankubhuto. ","ps3.10:16.12":"Tam kissa hetu? ","ps3.10:16.13":"Tatha hi so bhavanasampanno adhitthanasampanno ajivasampanno. ","ps3.10:17.1":"Byapadam pajahanto abyapadam bhavetiti—","ps3.10:17.2":"bhavanasampanno …pe… ","ps3.10:17.3":"thinamiddham pajahanto alokasannam bhavetiti—","ps3.10:17.4":"bhavanasampanno …pe… ","ps3.10:17.5":"uddhaccam pajahanto avikkhepam bhavetiti—","ps3.10:17.6":"bhavanasampanno …pe… ","ps3.10:17.7":"vicikiccham pajahanto dhammavavatthanam bhavetiti—","ps3.10:17.8":"bhavanasampanno …pe… ","ps3.10:17.9":"avijjam pajahanto vijjam bhavetiti—","ps3.10:17.10":"bhavanasampanno …pe… ","ps3.10:17.11":"aratim pajahanto pamojjam bhavetiti—","ps3.10:17.12":"bhavanasampanno …pe… ","ps3.10:17.13":"nivarane pajahanto pathamam jhanam bhavetiti—","ps3.10:17.14":"bhavanasampanno …pe… ","ps3.10:17.15":"sabbakilese pajahanto arahattamaggam bhavetiti—","ps3.10:17.16":"bhavanasampanno. ","ps3.10:17.17":"Arahattamaggavasena cittam adhitthatiti—","ps3.10:17.18":"adhitthanasampanno. ","ps3.10:17.19":"Svayam evam bhavanasampanno adhitthanasampanno samam jivati, no visamam; ","ps3.10:17.20":"samma jivati, no miccha; ","ps3.10:17.21":"visuddham jivati, no kilitthanti—","ps3.10:17.22":"ajivasampanno. ","ps3.10:17.23":"Svayam evam bhavanasampanno adhitthanasampanno ajivasampanno yannadeva parisam upasankamati—","ps3.10:17.24":"yadi khattiyaparisam yadi brahmanaparisam yadi gahapatiparisam yadi samanaparisam—","ps3.10:17.25":"visarado upasankamati amankubhuto. ","ps3.10:17.26":"Tam kissa hetu? ","ps3.10:17.27":"Tatha hi so bhavanasampanno adhitthanasampanno ajivasampannoti. ","ps3.10:17.28":"Matikakatha nitthita. ","ps3.10:17.29":"Pannavaggo tatiyo. ","ps3.10:17.30":"Tassuddanam ","ps3.10:18.1":"Panna iddhi abhisamayo, ","ps3.10:18.2":"viveko cariyapancamo; ","ps3.10:18.3":"Patihari samasisi, ","ps3.10:18.4":"satipatthana vipassana; ","ps3.10:18.5":"Tatiye pannavaggamhi, ","ps3.10:18.6":"matikaya ca te dasati. ","ps3.10:19.1":"Mahavaggo yuganaddho, ","ps3.10:19.2":"pannavaggo ca namato; ","ps3.10:19.3":"Tayova vagga imamhi, ","ps3.10:19.4":"patisambhidapakarane. ","ps3.10:20.1":"Anantanayamaggesu, ","ps3.10:20.2":"gambhiro sagarupamo; ","ps3.10:20.3":"Nabhanca tarakakinnam, ","ps3.10:20.4":"thulo jatassaro yatha; ","ps3.10:20.5":"Kathikanam visalaya, ","ps3.10:20.6":"yoginam nanajotananti. ","ps3.10:20.7":"Patisambhidamaggapali nitthita. "}